node.text:
Based on several leaks and rumors these AirPods 3 clones were created! In this unboxing I give you a closer look at them! As you can see they look like a combination of the AirPods 2 and AirPods Pro and won’t come with replaceable Ear Tips. Funny to see this manufacturer used my AirPods 3 concept on the packaging! The AirPods 3 are expected to come somewhere in the coming months, likely September or October!
________

Magic Mouse mini was created with a new type of design to enhance the portability and work performance of users. All the gestures used on the trackpad are available, and the iPad and MacBook can be carried around more lightly. The material is made of nano suction material so that it can be freely attached, and the height of the mouse can be adjusted.

node.text: Apple just announced the new iPad Pro featuring the Apple Silicon M1 chip, Thunderbolt, 5G support, 12MP ultra wide front camera, 2TB storage option, up to 16GB RAM, and more. So the iPhone 12S Pro camera will get one of the biggest upgrades ever seen on an iPhone! Specifically some of the main features we could expect:⁣
⁣
• Improved low light performance⁣
• Sensor-shift stabilization⁣
• Ultra Wide Lens improvements⁣
• Minor Wide-angle Lens update⁣
• Video Portrait Mode⁣
• Astrophotography capability⁣
• Improved noise cancellation⁣
• New ProRes video format⁣
⁣
Also don’t forget that the camera design as a whole will be significantly bigger on the back! Do you use your iPhone camera a lot and what are your thoughts on these upgrades?⁣
